==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*σανδάλιον / sandalion / san-dal'-ee-on 

===Etymology===
*Neuter of a derivative of [[σάνδαλον]] sandalon (a “sandal”; of uncertain origin); 

===Noun===
'''σανδάλιον'''

# a [[slipper]] or sole pad: - [[sandal]].

